        <h2>Harvard University</h2>

        <p>
    <strong>Website:</strong>
    <a href="https://www.harvard.edu/" target="_blank">https://www.harvard.edu/</a>
</p>


        <p>
            Harvard University is one of the most prestigious universities in the world,
            located in Cambridge, Massachusetts, United States. Founded in 1636, it is
            the oldest institution of higher learning in the United States. Harvard is
            highly competitive and selective, receiving thousands of applications each
            year. Applicants are expected to have strong academic records, excellent
            standardized test scores, and compelling personal statements.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Academic Excellence:</strong> Harvard offers rigorous academic
                programs in arts, sciences, humanities, engineering, law, medicine, and
                business, led by world-renowned faculty members and scholars.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Research and Innovation:</strong> The university is a major center
                for research and innovation, focusing on solving global challenges and
                securing significant research funding.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Campus Life:</strong> Harvard has a vibrant and diverse campus
                community with numerous student organizations, clubs, sports, cultural
                events, and social activities.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Global Reputation:</strong> Harvard is consistently recognized as
                one of the top universities in the world, with strong international
                partnerships.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Alumni Network:</strong> Harvard has a powerful alumni network
                that includes influential leaders in business, politics, academia, and
                other fields.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>


<!-- MMSU Modal -->
<div id="mmsuModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <span class="close" onclick="closeModal('mmsuModal')">&times;</span>
        <h2>Mariano Marcos State University (MMSU)</h2>

        <p>
    <strong>Website:</strong>
    <a href="https://www.mmsu.edu.ph/" target="_blank">https://mmsu.edu.ph/</a>
</p>


        <p>
            Mariano Marcos State University (MMSU) is a premier state university located
            in Ilocos Norte, Philippines. Established in 1978, MMSU has grown to become
            a leading institution of higher learning in the northern part of the country.
            Its main campus is located in Batac, Ilocos Norte, with several satellite
            campuses across the province. MMSU is a great option for students pursuing
            higher education in the Philippines.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Academic Excellence:</strong> MMSU offers a wide range of undergraduate
                and graduate programs in agriculture, engineering, arts, sciences, and business,
                and is known for its strong academic standards.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Research and Innovation:</strong> MMSU serves as a hub for research and
                innovation, focusing on regional and national development challenges with support
                from government and international institutions.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Community Engagement:</strong> The university is deeply committed to
                community service through extension programs, disaster preparedness initiatives,
                and environmental conservation efforts.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Campus Life:</strong> MMSU offers a vibrant campus life with student
                organizations, clubs, sports activities, and cultural events.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Beautiful Campus:</strong> The campus is known for its scenic beauty,
                lush greenery, modern facilities, and peaceful learning environment.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Oxford Modal -->
<div id="oxfordModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <span class="close" onclick="closeModal('oxfordModal')">&times;</span>
        <h2>University of Oxford</h2>

        <p>
    <strong>Website:</strong>
    <a href="https://www.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">https://www.ox.ac.uk/</a>
</p>


        <p>
            The University of Oxford is one of the oldest and most prestigious universities
            in the world, located in Oxford, England. Founded in the 11th century, it is
            considered one of the top universities globally. Oxford University is highly
            competitive and selective, and admission is typically quite challenging.
            The university receives thousands of applications each year. Applicants are
            expected to have a strong academic record, excellent standardized test scores,
            and a compelling personal statement.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Academic Excellence:</strong> Oxford is renowned for its rigorous
                academic programs across a wide range of disciplines, including arts,
                sciences, humanities, engineering, law, and medicine. The university is
                home to many world-renowned faculty members and scholars.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Collegiate System:</strong> Oxford is a collegiate university,
                meaning students are affiliated with one of the university’s 39 colleges.
                Each college provides a unique community and academic experience.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Research and Innovation:</strong> Oxford is a major center for
                research and innovation, with a focus on addressing global challenges and
                conducting groundbreaking research projects supported by significant
                funding.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Campus Life:</strong> The Oxford campus is a vibrant and diverse
                community with numerous student organizations, clubs, and activities.
                Students can participate in sports, cultural events, and social gatherings.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Global Reputation:</strong> Oxford is widely recognized as one of
                the top universities in the world, with strong partnerships with leading
                institutions across the globe and a diverse international student body.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>


<!-- UP Modal -->
<div id="upModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <span class="close" onclick="closeModal('upModal')">&times;</span>
        <h2>University of the Philippines (UP)</h2>

        <p>
    <strong>Website:</strong>
    <a href="https://up.edu.ph/" target="_blank">https://up.edu.ph/</a>
</p>

        <p>
            The University of the Philippines (UP) is a premier state university system in
            the Philippines, renowned for its academic excellence, research, and community
            engagement. It is considered one of the top universities in Asia and is often
            referred to as the national university of the Philippines. The main campuses
            are located in Diliman, Quezon City; Los Baños, Laguna; and Baguio City. UP is
            highly competitive and selective, making it a prestigious choice for higher
            education in the country.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Academic Excellence:</strong> UP offers a wide range of undergraduate
                and graduate programs in arts, sciences, humanities, engineering, medicine,
                law, and agriculture, supported by rigorous academic standards and highly
                qualified faculty.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Research and Innovation:</strong> UP is a major center for research
                and innovation in the Philippines, contributing significantly to national
                development through groundbreaking research projects.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Community Engagement:</strong> The university is deeply committed
                to public service through extension programs, disaster relief efforts,
                and environmental conservation initiatives.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Campus Life:</strong> UP has multiple campuses across the country,
                each with its own unique culture, offering students various extracurricular
                activities such as sports, clubs, and organizations.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Global Reputation:</strong> UP is internationally recognized and
                maintains strong partnerships with top universities around the world,
                attracting students from different countries.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>


